402
00:28:10.303 --> 00:28:12.305
Odlicno. To je moj sin.

403
00:28:17.018 --> 00:28:19.020
Mozemo li da jedemo?

404
00:28:31.782 --> 00:28:34.952
- Ove vracam.
- Uredu. Hvala.


405
00:28:52.595 --> 00:28:55.556
- sta ja radim u biblioteci?
- Joey.


406
00:28:56.390 --> 00:28:59.351
Kakav je to parfem?
Tako lepo mirises.


407
00:28:59.519 --> 00:29:00.729
- Joey.
- sta?


408
00:29:00.895 --> 00:29:03.106
Ne ovde. Izbacice nas napolje.

409
00:29:03.272 --> 00:29:04.732
Dobro.

410
00:29:05.525 --> 00:29:09.654
- Uzmi knjigu, i idemo odavde.
